list.abstract: OTHER（英[ˈʌðə]，美[ˈʌðər]），英语单词，作形容词为另一个；其他的；别的等。作动词为将…看作异类；以异类对待。短语搭配有each other（互相）。例句有“They needed to be aroused one way or the other, and they preferred good news to bad.（他们需要以某种方式被唤醒，他们更喜欢好消息而不是坏消息。）” OTHER的形容词近义词有another、else。反义词有same。

yingyinNormal.en: Then, why don't you? All the other fairies fly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那为什么你没有？其他的仙女都会飞。

yingyinNormal.en: While the butter mixture melts, blend together the other ingredients.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当奶油融化时，加入其他的原料搅拌一下。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, what if no one goes for the blonde? We don't get in each other's way, and we don't insult the other girls.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是，如果我们都不去找那美女。我们就不会彼此阻挠，也不会羞辱其他的女孩。

yingyinNormal.en: But other people, they have faces like us. Those are pictures of real things, and all the other stuff you see on there, that's real, too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但其他的人有着和我们相似的脸的那些人，那些画面里的人是真实存在的，还有你在电视上看到的其他事物也是真实的。

yingyinNormal.en: But that's not to say that they didn’t have other passions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但这不代表他们没有其他的喜好。

yingyinNormal.en: What's up, other owners? What's up, Ace? Our sales, by 400%!
yingyinNormal.zh: 其他的老板们，你们好吗？艾斯，你好吗？我们的业绩成长了400%呢！

yingyinNormal.en: It's homicidal by design. Walter kills other hosts all the time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 本来的设计就是谋杀犯，沃尔特一直都杀其他的接待员。

yingyinNormal.en: The other governors and I have decided it's time for you to step aside.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我还有其他的理事都认为该是你走的时候了。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: $14, huh? Put it back in your pocket, or I'll find some other place to put it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 14块？放回你的口袋里，要不然我会找个其他的地方搁。

yingyinNormal.en: And the other Dutch people? They come from somewhere near the Netherlands, right?
yingyinNormal.zh: 其他的荷兰人呢？他们是荷兰附近来的吧？

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, I imagine it's much like all the other ones. And I'm leaving first thing, El.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想和其他的聚会没什么区别。明天我一早要出门，小艾。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, what if the puppy said, "Help me Chandler. All the other puppies pick on me."
yingyinNormal.zh: 要是那只小狗说“钱德救救我，其他的狗狗都欺负我”。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll be friends with the other interns. They'll show me how to do it in the morning.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我可以关注其他的实习生，他们明天早上会教我。

yingyinNormal.en: Riley, it's not enough to go through life without considering the other point of view.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莱丽，把其他的想法不当回事是没办法顺利度过一生的。

yingyinNormal.en: The other defendants have made an allegation against you. Have you heard this allegation?
yingyinNormal.zh: 其他的被告对你作出一项指证。你听说过这项指证吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Thanksgiving is my favorite holiday, because, more than any other, it is uniquely American.
yingyinNormal.zh: 感恩节是我非常喜爱的节日，因为比起其他的节日它更特殊,它是美国人独有的。

yingyinNormal.en: There're seven other planets that go around our sun. Does anyone know what they are called? Mercury.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们的太阳旁边还有七个其他的行星。大家知道这些行星叫什么吗？叫水星。

yingyinNormal.en: George, Richard and Edmond haven't found any eggs. I wonder where the other eggs are. Chocolate egg.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治，理查德和埃德蒙一个彩蛋也没找到。你们想知道其他的彩蛋在哪吗？巧克力彩蛋。

yingyinNormal.en: We're sharing lessons learned, so other hospitals don't repeat the mistakes that happened in Dallas.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们在分享着学到的知识，因此其他的医院不会再犯在达拉斯所犯的错误。

yingyinNormal.en: So, do you have any other possibilities? Oh yeah, well there's the possibility that I won't make rent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你还有其他的机会吗？有，我很可能会付不出房租来。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: adv. 不然；否则；在其他方面；除此之外；别样；以另外方式；或；另外

sense_info_list.en: being the one (as of two or more) left

examination_example.sentence: It's also a good idea to delay the conversation if you are in a meeting or <highlight>other</highlight> public space.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你在会议或其他公共场所，推迟谈话也是个好主意。

examination_example.sentence: Be open to hearing <highlight>other</highlight> opinions.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 虚心听取别人的意见。

examination_example.sentence: Watch out for how they verbalize with <highlight>others</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 注意他们是如何与他人交谈的。

examination_example.sentence: To be contradictory to each <highlight>other</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 相互矛盾。

examination_example.sentence: Now we can understand each <highlight>other</highlight>'s positions and recognize our shared values, since we both care about needy workers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 现在我们可以理解彼此的立场，并认识到我们共同的价值观，因为我们都关心贫困的工人。

examination_example.sentence: "We reason together, challenge, revise, and complete each <highlight>other</highlight>'s reasoning and each <highlight>other</highlight>'s conceptions of reason."
examination_example.sentence_trans: “我们一起推理，挑战，修改，完善彼此的推理和彼此的理性概念。”

word_usage.usage: other 指不同类的人或事物，如： it will benefit other Asian countries（这将使其他亚洲国家受益）。当谈论两个人或事物中的第二个时，用 the other 或 the other one。当谈论数个人或事物中剩余的部分时，通常用the others。another 指同类的另一个人或事物，后面常跟可数名词单数、one、few或者大于1的数字。

examination_example.sentence: He met many tourists from <highlight>other</highlight> countries.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他遇到了许多来自其他国家的游客。

examination_example.sentence: It wasn't their skill set or <highlight>other</highlight> merits that got them the job.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 并不是他们的技能或其他优点让他们得到了这份工作。

examination_example.sentence: Genetic selection is a way of exerting influence over <highlight>others</highlight>, "the ultimate collective control of human destinies," as writer H. G. Wells put it.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 基因选择是对他人施加影响的一种方式，正如作家H. G. Wells所说，“人类命运的最终集体控制”。

examination_example.sentence: It infringes on intellectual property rights of <highlight>others</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它侵犯了他人的知识产权。

examination_example.sentence: It is likely to create traffic jams in <highlight>other</highlight> places.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 很可能会造成其他地方的交通堵塞。

examination_example.sentence: Still, it is to be hoped that the Scottish government's bold move will prompt <highlight>others</highlight> to act.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 尽管如此，人们还是希望苏格兰政府的大胆举措能促使其他政府采取行动。

word_usage.usage:
other表示“其他的”，后常跟复数名词或不可数名词。
示例：Are there any other questions? 
还有其他问题没有？

other前如有this, that, some, any, each, every, no, none, one等词时，也可修饰单数名词。
示例：I can't see you now—some other time, maybe.
我现在不能见你——也许别的时候吧。

other/the other/others/the others的区别：
(1) 泛指用other，后接复数名词（如other boys 其他男孩）。
(2) 特指用the other，后接复数名词（如the other boys 特指其余的男孩）。
(3) others表达泛指的复数意义，其后不接名词（others=other+复数名词）。
(4) the others表达特指的复数意义，其后也不接名词（the others=the other+复数名词）。

examination_example.sentence: Make a point, and make it safe for <highlight>others</highlight> to do the same.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 明确自己的观点，并确保其他人也能安全效仿。

examination_example.sentence: If <highlight>others</highlight> benefit in the process, and I get some reward too, does it really matter where my motivation lies?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果别人在这个过程中受益，而我也得到了一些奖励，那我的动机是什么真的重要吗？

examination_example.sentence: Some of us were confident and eager to take part in the class activity, <highlight>others</highlight> were nervous and anxious.

word_usage.usage:

Two other men came to cheer the Chinese team.
